Multiple domains is hosted on single IP adress.

1.Password reset poisoning
2.Web cache poisoining

client ----------------- server

1.DNS resoulution
2.TCP connection
3.Host header 

Multiple domain on single IP is called (Virtual Hosting.)

1.Virtual Host
A server hosting multiple websites having different domain for each.
Multiple domain single ip
Content is served based on host header
If host header is manipulated ,server may serve u attackers malicious content
1.Password reset poisioning
2.Web cache poisioning

Host header injection(HHI)
